{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":97,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shang_xiu_xun","text":"商场主，尚有五里水路就可抵竟陵，这是探看敌情的千载良机，看！那山丘上便有数十个军营。","tone":"平静","chapter":119,"line_start":3,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"你该知道自己还是学徒级的舵手，竟不集中精神，却在左顾右盼，万一撞翻了船，岂非教扬州双雄英名尽丧。","tone":"调侃","chapter":119,"line_start":9,"line_end":11},{"speaker":"char_shang_xiu_xun","speaker_name":"商秀洵","listener":null,"text":"人人此时紧张得要命，你却还有心情开玩笑，小心如此托大会坏事呢。","tone":"无奈","chapter":119,"line_start":13,"line_end":15},{"speaker":"char_shang_xiu_xun","speaker_name":"商秀洵","listener":null,"text":"还不泊岸！","tone":"焦急","chapter":119,"line_start":31,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"若在这里泊岸，只会陷入苦战和被歼之局，眼前之计，只有冒险穿过敌方船阵，直抵城外码头，才有一线生机。","tone":"认真","chapter":119,"line_start":33,"line_end":35},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"这叫出其不意，看似凶险，其实却是最可行的方法。","tone":"认真","chapter":119,"line_start":37,"line_end":39},{"speaker":"char_shang_xiu_xun","speaker_name":"商秀洵","listener":null,"text":"准备火箭！","tone":"厉声","chapter":119,"line_start":43,"line_end":43},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"放火烧船！","tone":"激动","chapter":119,"line_start":45,"line_end":47},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"弟兄们，布盾阵。","tone":"厉声","chapter":119,"line_start":63,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"准备逃生！","tone":"厉声","chapter":119,"line_start":97,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_shang_xiu_xun","text":"船尾也着火了呢！","tone":"焦急","chapter":119,"line_start":85,"line_end":87}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xu_zi_ling","name":"徐子陵","alias":[],"identity":"双龙之一，飞马牧场盟友","faction":"飞马牧场","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"双龙之一，与寇仲并