{"segment":2,"line_start":98,"line_end":193,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_qian_yun","speaker_name":"钱云","listener":"char_shang_xiu_xun","text":"真想不到场主忽然凤驾光临，当日闻知四大寇联手攻打牧场，敝庄主还想出兵往援，却因江淮军犯境，才被迫打消此意。","tone":"陈述","chapter":119,"line_start":191,"line_end":193},{"speaker":"char_liang_zhi","speaker_name":"梁治","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"钱将军难道不知贵庄主派了一位叫贾良的人到我们处要求援兵吗？他还持有贵庄主画押盖印的亲笔信呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":119,"line_start":197,"line_end":199},{"speaker":"char_qian_yun","speaker_name":"钱云","listener":"char_liang_zhi","text":"竟有此事。末将从没听庄主提过，更不识有一个叫贾良的人，何况我们一向惯以飞鸽传书互通信息，何须遣人求援。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":119,"line_start":201,"line_end":203},{"speaker":"char_shang_xiu_xun","speaker_name":"商秀洵","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"方庄主呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":119,"line_start":207,"line_end":207},{"speaker":"char_qian_yun","speaker_name":"钱云","listener":"char_shang_xiu_xun","text":"末将已遣人知会敝庄主，该快来了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":119,"line_start":209,"line_end":209},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"我们立即去拜会方庄主，请钱兄派人领路。","tone":"认真","chapter":119,"line_start":211,"line_end":211},{"speaker":"char_qian_yun","speaker_name":"钱云","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"还未请教两位大名。","tone":"陈述","chapter":119,"line_start":213,"line_end":213},{"speaker":"char_shang_xiu_xun","speaker_name":"商秀洵","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"他是寇仲，另一位是徐子陵，都是庄主的朋友。","tone":"低语","chapter":119,"line_start":215,"line_end":217},{"speaker":"char_qian_yun","speaker_name":"钱云","listener":null,"text":"原来是你们两人，庄主有令，立杀无赦！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":119,"line_start":219,"line_end":221},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"小陵啊！真是笑死我呢！方庄主不知是否另有一个绰号叫糊涂蛇，竟给阴癸派的妖女婠婠弄了手脚，先是断送了自己亲弟的性命，又杀了自己手下头号猛将，更给她盗得符印冒名写信布下陷阱，现在还要视友为敌，硬要杀死我们两大好人，你说是否好笑呢？","tone":"大笑","chapter":119,"line_start":237,"line_end":241},{"speaker":"char_qian_yun","speaker_name":"钱云","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"竟敢诬陷婠婠夫人…我…","tone":"愤怒","chapter":119,"line_start":243,"line_end":243},{"speaker":"char_shang_xiu_xun","speaker_name":"商秀洵","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"闭嘴！现今杜伏威枕军城外，内则有妖女当道，你这糊涂蛇不但不晓得忠言谏主，还要先来个和我们自相残杀。哼！若我们拂袖而去，看你们如何收场。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":119,"line_start":245,"line_end":249},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"钱将军不是也迷上那阴癸派的妖女吧！","tone":"调侃","chapter":119,"line_start":251,"line_end":253},{"speaker":"char_lao_jiang","speaker_name":"老将","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"寇爷口口声声说婠婠夫人乃阴癸派的妖女，不知有何凭据呢？","tone":"严肃","chapter":119,"line_start":255,"line_end":257},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"只要让我们与婠婠对质，自可真相大白，钱将军不是连这亦办不到吧！","tone":"淡然","chapter":119,"line_start":259,"line_end":261},{"speaker":"char_liang_zhi","speaker_name":"梁治","listener":"char_qian_yun","text":"若妄动干戈，徒令亲者痛仇者快，钱将军好该三思这是否智者所为。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":119,"line_start":263,"line_end":265},{"speaker":"char_qian_yun","speaker_name":"钱云","listener":null,"text":"既有场主为他两人出头，小将亦难以作主，惟有待庄主定夺好了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":119,"line_start":271,"line_end":273}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_qian_yun","name":"钱云","alias":[],"identity":"竟陵城守将","faction":"竟陵独霸山庄","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"竟陵城守将，方泽滔麾下，奉命拦截寇仲和徐子陵","personality":{"traits":["服从","耿直","忠诚","缺乏主见","勇猛"],"speech_style":"恭敬正式","temperament":"耿直"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_fang_ze_tao","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"忠心执行"},{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"对手","intensity":60,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"初识对峙"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[119],"source_refs":[{"chapter":119,"line_start":191,"line_end":193,"text":"钱云仍未知道两人身分"}]},{"id":"char_lao_jiang","name":"老将","alias":[],"identity":"竟陵城老将","faction":"竟陵独霸山庄","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"竟陵城年约六十的老将，质疑寇仲对婠婠的指控","personality":{"traits":["老练","沉稳","谨慎","有主见","公正"],"speech_style":"严肃正式","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_qian_yun","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同僚"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[119],"source_refs":[{"chapter":119,"line_start":255,"line_end":257,"text":"他身后的人中走出一个年约六十的老将"}]},{"id":"char_fang_ze_tao","name":"方泽滔","alias":["庄主"],"identity":"竟陵独霸山庄庄主","faction":"竟陵独霸山庄","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"竟陵独霸山庄庄主，被婠婠蒙蔽，下令追杀寇仲和徐子陵","personality":{"traits":["刚愎","受蒙蔽","重情","优柔","受制于人"],"speech_style":"威严","temperament":"刚愎"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_qian_yun","type":"主仆","intensity":75,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"上下级"},{"target":"char_wan_wan","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"受蒙蔽"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[119],"source_refs":[{"chapter":119,"line_start":163,"line_end":163,"text":"守城的乃方泽滔麾下的将领钱云"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_jing_ling_shan_zhuang","name":"独霸山庄","type":"帮派","location":"loc_jing_ling","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"竟陵城的武装势力，由方泽滔统领，正被杜伏威围困","source_refs":[{"chapter":119,"line_start":163,"line_end":163,"text":"守城的乃方泽滔麾下的将领钱云"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
